                <h1>Find Windows 7 Wallpaper Location Easily</h1>
                <p>Windows 7 wallpapers are stored in the C:\Windows\Web\Wallpaper directory by default. You can access these images by navigating to this folder using Windows Explorer. Here, you'll find a variety of wallpapers that come pre-installed with the OS. To set a new wallpaper, right-click on your chosen image and select 'Set as desktop background.'</p>
